      <![CDATA[<h3 id="开幕—-重生了我山姆王哈哈哈哈"><a href="#开幕—-重生了我山姆王哈哈哈哈" class="headerlink" title="开幕—-重生了我山姆王哈哈哈哈"></a>开幕—-重生了我山姆王哈哈哈哈</h3><figure class="article-figure is-sized" style="max-width:605px"><a class="gallery-item" href="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260319202006_.jpg" data-lightbox="article" data-group="post-media" data-caption=""><img src="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260319202006_.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20260319202006_.jpg" loading="lazy"></a></figure><p>本次游玩我是租赁了一台ps5slim进行游玩，画质非常好，遗憾的点就是我无法登陆自己的账号进行成就的解锁以及存档的保存，所以这一点非常的伤心。<br>接下来是我在游玩过程中拍摄的一些好看的图片，让我们一起欣赏把！！！</p><figure class="article-figure is-groupable"><a class="gallery-item" href="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260320114953.jpg" data-lightbox="article" data-group="post-media" data-caption=""><img src="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260320114953.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20260320114953.jpg" loading="lazy"></a></figure><p>话说，小岛秀夫是不是已经把这两位当cp了，如果是这样的话我很同意哈哈哈哈哈！！！<br>sam爸爸 fragile妈妈 还有luo小宝宝 ，真是有爱的一家！！！</p><figure class="article-figure is-groupable"><a class="gallery-item" href="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260322111420.jpg" data-lightbox="article" data-group="post-media" data-caption=""><img src="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260322111420.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20260322111420.jpg" loading="lazy"></a></figure><p>哈哈哈哈哈，不是哥们我请问！！！谁看见这个不想截一张图下来呢？真绝了</p><figure class="article-figure is-groupable"><a class="gallery-item" href="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260322140326.jpg" data-lightbox="article" data-group="post-media" data-caption=""><img src="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260322140326.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20260322140326.jpg" loading="lazy"></a></figure><p>这就是合金装备的魅力吗有点好看的</p><figure class="article-figure is-groupable"><a class="gallery-item" href="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260322192651.jpg" data-lightbox="article" data-group="post-media" data-caption=""><img src="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260322192651.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20260322192651.jpg" loading="lazy"></a></figure><p>咱姐的战斗脸还是太有说法了！！！！没招了</p><figure class="article-figure is-groupable"><a class="gallery-item" href="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260324222506_.jpg" data-lightbox="article" data-group="post-media" data-caption=""><img src="/obsidian-assets/assets/deathstranding/DEATH%20STRANDING%202_%20ON%20THE%20BEACH_20260324222506_.jpg" alt="DEATH STRANDING 2_ ON THE BEACH_20260324222506_.jpg" loading="lazy"></a></figure><p>太美了！！！fragile</p>]]>
